Class AreaDeliveriesOperatorController

java.lang.Object
clientGUIControllers.AreaDeliveriesOperatorController
public class AreaDeliveriesOperatorController extends Object
Area Deliveries Operator Controller Contains all the functionality to move the employee to the screen required to perform the various actions possible.

  • Method Details

    • initialize

      public void initialize()
      The initialize method is used to set visibility of the buttons , images and labels. In addition, this method checks if to this worker have a second role as a customer, and according to his second role shows the appropriate button.

    • additionalPermissionPressed

      void additionalPermissionPressed(javafx.event.ActionEvent event)
      Parameters:
      event - - additional permission button pressed. The method checks if the worker has second role as customer and if he have take him to the appropriate screen.
